OL,3,CPerson arrested after collison leaves
OL,4,Ccar in flames
OL,6,FA person has been arrested after a
OL,7,Fcollision between two vehicles along
OL,8,FJersey's Five Mile Road on Friday (1
OL,9,FMay) evening.
OL,11,FOne of the vehicles went up in flames
OL,12,Fas a result, with smoke seen from
OL,13,Facross St Ouen.
OL,15,FPolice were called to the incident
OL,16,Fopposite the La Braye restaurant just
OL,17,Fafter 18:00.
OL,19,FTwo people were taken to hospital for
OL,20,Fminor injuries.
